research_municipality_step.notes: Information gathered from the official City of Corsicana website, Texas Municipal League City Officials Directory, and Texas State Directory Online. There were some discrepancies in older search results regarding the Mayor and council members, but the most recent and official sources consistently list Joe Hill as Mayor and Jim Pannell, Shayla Johnson, Chris Woolsey, and Jeff Smith as Council Members for Precincts 1, 2, 3, and 4 respectively.
